Hello there, here are a few commands you can use to manage support threads in Slack.

*Tracking and Resolving*

`track` Start tracking a thread, and create a GitHub issue.
`title` Set the title for the GitHub issue.
`resolve` Stop tracking a thread, and close its GitHub issue.

*Categories/Labels*

`add category` Add a category to this thread, and a label to its GitHub issue.
`list categories` List the categories added to this thread.

*Links and Documentation*

`add link` Add a link to this thread.
`list links` List the links added to this thread.
`remove link` Remove a link from this thread.

*Help*

`help` Show this help message.
